{"tid":2373483,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同我一樣係咁","createTime":"2021-01-20T13:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T14:15:01.000Z","uid":300420,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"73d6ef019c3e6c854b857892ae8e67c640a2a49f","tid":2373483,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:11:12.000Z","msg":"十幾歲人 相貌平平 沉默寡言<br />\n入咗間平凡嘅大學 讀一科自己唔係幾鍾意嘅科<br />\n個人既冇專業技能 又冇過人嘅成就<br />\n但係又唔想歸於平凡 唔想喺香港做社會機器嘅螺絲<br />\n想出去見識多啲野 接觸多啲好人<br />\n<br />\n對未來有啲迷惘 唔知幾年之後可以做咩好<br />\n有冇廢青一齊圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ed42697861324cc4fd43b54bc9c6d28ad38373","tid":2373483,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"a28466fdb50c0b817070e8c22f33ba61c66b1379","tid":2373483,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3ed42697861324cc4fd43b54bc9c6d28ad38373","tid":2373483,"uid":29836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:12:38.000Z","msg":"Cusis drop到科未<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6b24d0e355eb398003303b2cdc83d11dfe3748e","tid":2373483,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7bfaa2d7d6eed02f69db371f5a7ac723c479843","tid":2373483,"uid":300420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6b24d0e355eb398003303b2cdc83d11dfe3748e","tid":2373483,"uid":355064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T13:48:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6010a84080b98e261f848ba2f3